high_descs: Turn to the right and turn left around the counter. Stop mid way and face the counter to the left.
Pick up the tomato in the middle of the counter.
Hold the tomato and turn to the left and then right. Turn right to move to the stove and look up to the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the tomato inside. Shut the door and then open the door. Take out the tomato and shut the door.
Hold the tomato and look down, turn to the right and then right again to move to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the tomato inside. Shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Heat and then chill a tomato.

high_descs: Walk around the right side of the counter and turn left to face the tomato on the counter.
Pick up the tomato on the counter.
Walk around the counter and to the right to face the microwave over the stove.
Heat the tomato in the microwave and remove it.
Turn around and walk forward to face the fridge.
Place the tomato in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To heat a tomato and place it in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right and then hang a left to face the tomato on the counter.
Pick up the tomato from the counter.
Turn right and walk around the counter, turning right again to reach the microwave above the stove.
Heat up the tomato in the microwave, removing it afterwards.
Turn around to walk to the fridge.
Put the tomato in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Heat up a tomato in the microwave to put in the fridge.
